=\"_blank\">Hot to install GUI Desktop environment on ubuntu linux</a>&nbsp;- KDE , Gnome</span></li>\n	<li><a href=\"https://wizardforcel.gitbooks.io/w3school-linux/content/171.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">W3CSchool - Linux 教程</span></a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"http://120.105.184.250/peiyuli/network-2/x-window.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">X - Window System</span></a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.lijyyh.com/2015/12/x-window-introduction-to-x-window-system_17.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">X - Window 簡介</span></a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u010454729/article/details/39778213\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ubuntu - xinetd簡介&nbsp;</span></a>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/etc/service 設定檔</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">20190620</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.twblogs.net/a/5c376016bd9eee35b3a59984\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Xorg-Xserver 相關解析</span></span></a></li>\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.itread01.com/p/1390581.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Linux 在遠端XServer 上顯示圖形介面</span></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">20190619</span></span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><a href=\"https://www.opencli.com/linux/linux-boot-process\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Linux 開機流程</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\">PAM module 管理帳密</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">20190522&nbsp;</span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><a href=\"https://www.lijyyh.com/2012/07/pam-managing-account-security-with-pam.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">reference -&nbsp;使用PAM module manager account</span></a></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\">Linux -&nbsp;sysvinit</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">20190521&nbsp;</span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><a href=\"https://www.ibm.com/developerworks/cn/linux/1407_liuming_init1/index.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">reference - IBM</span></a></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>20190521</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>linux system V意思</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://f543711700.iteye.com/blog/1167656\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>20190508</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>linux .o .so .a 檔案意思</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">最近在unbuntu環境下開發代碼，由於很少使用linux開發環境，所以對linux編譯方面了解更少，關於.o, .a, .so文件和可執行文件一直很困惑</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">今天特意查了一下關於它們的區分：</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">.o就相當於windows裡的obj文件，一個.c或.cpp文件對應一個.o文件<br />\n	.a是好多個.o合在一起,用於靜態連接，即STATIC mode，多個.a可以鏈接生成一個exe的可執行文件<br />\n	.so是shared object,用於動態連接的,和windows的dll差不多，使用時才載入。</span></span><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>ubuntu 18.04 locale</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://samwhelp.github.io/note-ubuntu-18.04/read/howto/install/locale/\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>20190403</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>ubuntu 14 開機就執行</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>\n	<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">切換 tty 指令</span></span></p>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">chvt&nbsp;1 ~ 7 (tty1 ~ tty7&nbsp;)</span></p>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">reference </span></p>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"http://blog.vic.mh4u.org/2009/1224\" target=\"_blank\">ubuntu&nbsp;開機就執行</a>&nbsp;,&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://felix-lin.com/linux/debianubuntu-%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E9%96%8B%E6%A9%9F%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ubuntu&nbsp;開機自動執行程式</span></a></p>\n		</li>\n		<li>\n		<p><a href=\"http://blog.vic.mh4u.org/2009/1224\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ubuntu 開機流程</span></a></p>\n		</li>\n		<li>\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://blogger.liaohaha.tw/2012/06/ubuntuscript.html\" target=\"_blank\">ubuntu 開機後自動執行指定的script</a>&nbsp;</span></p>\n		</li>\n		<li>\n		<p><a href=\"https://codertw.com/%E4%BC%BA%E6%9C%8D%E5%99%A8/379414/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ubuntu14 開機設定啟動碼的方式</span></a></p>\n		</li>\n		<li>\n		<p><a href=\"http://www.linuxdiyf.com/viewarticle.php?id=102927\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">upstart ubuntu 啟動過程簡單原理</span></a></p>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">vi /etc/rc.local</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">於 exit 0 前面加入所需的命令</span></p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">你要先將所要執行的命令寫到一個 shell script 內.<br />\n	# vi test</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">將這個設定權限改為 755<br />\n	# chmod 755 /etc/init.d/test</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">將script加到開機啟動內<br />\n	# update-rc.d test default 90</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">其中90這個數字攸關開機的順序,如果你的服務是需要其他像網路的支援,數字就放大一點.</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">將這個 script 複製到 /etc/init.d 的目錄中.<br />\n	# cp test /etc/init.d/</span></p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">那麼改天不要它啟動時,要怎麼設定呢??<br />\n	不難,照以下做</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"># cd /etc/init.d</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"># update-rc.d -f test remove</span></p>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>20190319</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>ubuntu 18 &amp; centOS 7 </strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">ubuntu 18.04 英文裝android studio NDK</span></span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/skywang12345/archive/2013/05/23/3095013.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">reference</span></a>\n\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">安裝android-ndk-r15c</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">vim ~/.bashrc</span></li>\n			<li>\n			<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:16px\"># NDK_HOME必须和ndk的路径一致！\nexport NDK_HOME=/home/skywang/workspace/ndk/r7b/android-ndk-r7b\nexport PATH=$PATH:$NDK_HOME</span></pre>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">source ~/.bashrc</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">ubuntu 18.04 英文裝openjdk 8 ~ 11</span></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><a href=\"https://linuxize.com/post/install-java-on-ubuntu-18-04/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">reference</span></a>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">安裝openjdk 8</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">ubuntu 18.04 英文版裝注音輸入法&nbsp;</span></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://blog.xuite.net/yh96301/blog/287374341-Ubuntu+14.04%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E9%8D%B5%E7%9B%A4%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1gcin\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a></span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">安裝gcin&nbsp;</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">show detail path 顯示完整路徑</span></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">vim ~/.bashrc</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">export PS1=&#39;[u@h w]$&#39;</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">source ~/.bashrc</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>ubuntu 18&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"http://blog.lyhdev.com/2013/11/ubuntu-linux-apt-get-purge.html\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a></span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">移除 套件</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>20190227</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>BSP and Turn key</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><a href=\"http://speed.cis.nctu.edu.tw/~ydlin/miscpub/BSP_Turn-Key.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">reference</span></a></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">unix2dos&nbsp;, dos2unix&nbsp; (再用alias 改名)</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/a568953256/article/details/18559415\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">reference</span></a></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">开始不知道安装啥包，后来发现在tofrodos这个包里：</span>\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">sudo apt-get install tofrodos</span></p>\n\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">使用方法不是unix2dos和dos2unix了，而是todos 和fromdos了。</span></p>\n\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Converts DOS &lt;-&gt; Unix text files, alias tofromdos</span></p>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>核心移植</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">linux kernel 移植 無法開機及解決方案</span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://szlin.me/2017/05/17/unable-to-boot-with-linux-kernel/\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a> </span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"http://www.bkjia.com/Linuxjc/1296421.html\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a> - 核心移植</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">DTS - Device Tree Source&nbsp;</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/RadianceBlau/article/details/70800076\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a>&nbsp;基本知識</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">对ARM平台的相关code做出如下相关规范调整，这个也正是引入DTS的原因</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ARM的核心代码仍然保存在arch/arm目录下</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ARM SoC core architecture code保存在arch/arm目录下</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ARM SOC的周边外设模块的驱动保存在drivers目录下</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ARM SOC的特定代码在arch/arm/mach-xxx目录下</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ARM SOC board specific的代码被移除，由DeviceTree机制来负责传递硬件拓扑和硬件资源信息。</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">本质上，Device Tree改变了原来用hardcode方式将HW 配置信息嵌入到内核代码的方法，改用bootloader传递一个DB的形式。</span></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">如果我们认为kernel是一个black box，那么其输入参数应该包括：</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">a.识别platform的信息&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">b.runtime的配置参数&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">c.设备的拓扑结构以及特性</span></span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">对于嵌入式系统，在系统启动阶段，bootloader会加载内核并将控制权转交给内核，此外，还需要把上述的三个参数信息传递给kernel，以便kernel可以有较大的灵活性。</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在linux kernel中，Device Tree的设计目标就是如此。</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">DTS&nbsp; Discribtion</span></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Device Tree由一系列被命名的结点（node）和属性（property）组成，而结点本身可包含子结点。</span></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">谓属性，其实就是成对出现的name和value。在Device Tree中，可描述的信息包括（原先这些信息大多被hard code到kernel中）：</span></span><br />\n		&nbsp;\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">CPU的数量和类别</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">内存基地址和大小</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">总线和桥</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">外设连接</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">中断控制器和中断使用情况</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">GPIO控制器和GPIO使用情况</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">Clock控制器和Clock使用情况</span><br />\n			&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">它基本上就是画一棵电路板上CPU、总线、设备组成的树，Bootloader会将这棵树传递给内核，然后内核可以识别这棵树，并根据它展开出Linux内核中的platform_device、i2c_client、spi_device等设备，而这些设备用到的内存、IRQ等资源，也被传递给了内核，内核会将这些资源绑定给展开的相应的设备。</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>核心編譯</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ubuntu 18 更新核心</span>&nbsp;\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://www.itread01.com/content/1548585199.html\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a>&nbsp;- update linux kernel&nbsp;</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">kernel 進入點</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://danielmaker.github.io/blog/linux/start_kernel.html\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a>&nbsp;- kernel entry point&nbsp;</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>20190224&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>linux </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>開機流程</strong></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">完整linux系統，bootloader ，linux kernel&nbsp;</span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><a href=\"http://q248269673.pixnet.net/blog/post/69570279-%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E7%9A%84linux%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%EF%BC%9Abootloader%E3%80%81linux-kernel%EF%BC%88linux%E5%85%A7\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">reference</span></a></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>核心組成</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">分成5部分</span>\n\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">程序排成</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">行程間通訊</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">記憶體管理</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">虛擬檔案系統</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">網路介面</span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>核心啟動</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">cpu 過電</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">從CS:IP = FFFF:0000&nbsp;</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">入口處載入BIOS</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">載入 GRUB 到 0x07c00處(透過中斷0x19)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">載入核心映像 vmlinuz</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">真實模式入口function , (head.o 偏移512處)</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">arch/x86/boot/header.S:_start</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">真實模式main function </span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">arch/x86/boot/main.c:main()</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">arch/x86/boot/pm.c:go_to_protected_mode()</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">arch/x86/boot/pmjump.S:protected_mode_jump()</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">保護模式核心入口function (0x100000處) </span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">arch/x86/boot/compressed/head_32.S:startup_32()</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">arch/x86/kernel/head_32_.S:startup_32()</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;arch/x86/kernel/head_32.c:i386_start_kernel()</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Linux 核心啟動function (無關架構)</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">init/main.c:start_kernel()</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建立記憶體 rootfs :&nbsp;</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">fs/dcache.c:fs_caches_init()</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">fs/namespace.c:mnt_init()</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">核心初始化 function</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">init/main.c:reset_init()</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">init/main.c:kerenl_init()</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">載入RAM Disk</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">init/initramfs.c:populate_rootfs()</span>\n		<ol>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">cpio-initrd</span>\n			<ol>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/init</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">啟動/init 腳本</span>\n				<ul>\n					<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">init/main.c:init_post()</span></li>\n					<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">init/main.c:run_init_process()</span></li>\n				</ul>\n				</li>\n			</ol>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">image-inited</span>\n			<ol>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/init/do_mountss.c : prepare_namespace()</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/linuxrc</span></li>\n			</ol>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">偵測並掛載 procfs.sysfs : /proc/mounts , 讀取 /proc/cmdline , 啟動 udev:udevd-daemon</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">從/etc/fstab 掛載硬碟個分割區 ,&nbsp;掛載真正的根檔案系統啟動，使用者空間的 /sbin/init</span></li>\n		</ol>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">整體而言 , 核心啟動可以概括6個步驟</span>\n\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">真實模式的入口function _start() &nbsp;</span>\n\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在 header.S 中 ，這裡會進入眾所周知的main function , 他會複製bootloader 的各個參數，執行基本硬體設定，解析命令行參數。</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">保護模式的入口function start_32()&nbsp;</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在 compressed/header_32.S 中 , 這裡會解壓縮bzImage 核心映像，載入vmlinux核心檔案。</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">核心入口 function startup_32() : 在 kernel/header_32.S 中，就是所謂的程序0&nbsp;</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">它會進入架構無關的start_kernel() function , 即linux 核心啟動function ，start_kernel() 會做大量的核心初始化操作，解析核心啟動的命令行參數，並啟動一個核心執行緒來完成核心模組初始化的過程，然後進入閒置迴圈。</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li>&nbsp;</li>\n		<li>&nbsp;</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>20190221 Ubuntu 18.04</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>mysql</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ERROR 1045 (28000): Access denied for user &#39;root&#39;@&#39;localhost&#39; (using password: NO)</span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/5496d1329f6f\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a></span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><a href=\"https://computingforgeeks.com/install-mariadb-10-on-ubuntu-18-04-and-centos-7/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">install Mysql DB / Maria DB</span></a></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>c</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">packages</span></span>\n\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">MySQL API&nbsp;</span></span>\n\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;apt-get install libmysql++-dev </span>\n\n			<ul>\n				<li><a href=\"http://www.cppblog.com/lynch/archive/2016/03/11/196331.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">reference</span></a></li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">apt-get install libmysqlclient-dev</span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><a href=\"https://codertw.com/%E4%BC%BA%E6%9C%8D%E5%99%A8/378039/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">reference</span></a></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/usr/include/mysql 會有 mysql.h</span></li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>20190212 All Linux&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>MIME 類型</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Linux MIME 類型&nbsp;(</span><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/4617e8e600ad\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">reference</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\">)</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">MIME類型是用於描述文件的類型的一種表述方法，其將文件劃分為多種類型，方便對其進行統一的管理。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">MIME類型指定了文件的類型名稱，描述，圖標信息，同時通過與.destop應用程序描述文件整合，指定了文件的打開方式。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">MIME類型是被文件管理器使用，而不是Gnome或者Ubuntu系統本身。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">以GIMP的的.desktop為例說明：</span></li>\n	<li>\n	<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:16px\"><code>[Desktop Entry]\nVersion=1.0\nType=Application\nName=GNU Image Manipulation Program\nGenericName=Image Editor\nComment=Create images and edit photographs\nExec=gimp-2.7 %U\nTryExec=gimp-2.7\nIcon=gimp\nTerminal=false\nCategories=Graphics;2DGraphics;RasterGraphics;GTK;\nX-GNOME-Bugzilla-Bugzilla=GNOME\nX-GNOME-Bugzilla-Product=GIMP\nX-GNOME-Bugzilla-Component=General\nX-GNOME-Bugzilla-Version=2.7.2\nX-GNOME-Bugzilla-OtherBinaries=gimp-2.7\nStartupNotify=true\nMimeType=application/postscript;application/pdf;image/bmp;image/g3fax;image/gif;image/x-fits;image/pcx;image/x-portable-anymap;image/x-portable-bitmap;image/x-portable-graymap;image/x-portable-pixmap;image/x-psd;image/x-sgi;image/x-tga;image/x-xbitmap;image/x-xwindowdump;image/x-xcf;image/x-compressed-xcf;image/tiff;image/jpeg;image/x-psp;image/png;image/x-icon;image/x-xpixmap;image/svg+xml;application/pdf;image/x-wmf;image/jp2;image/jpeg2000;image/jpx;image/x-xcursor;\n</code></span></pre>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">MimeType字段說明了這個程序支持的MIME類型<br />\n	Exec字段說明了程序的打開方式，Exec字段最後的％U或％f很重要，其決定了這個程序時候能顯示在文件管理器的open with清單中。</span><br />\n	&nbsp;</p>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>20181122 (CentOS 7)</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>centOS 7 service (<a href=\"http://www.osslab.tw/index.php?title=User:Alang/Linux_%26_UNIX_%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98/Linux_service_list_(%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8)/Linux_on_virtual_machine\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a>)</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">cups.service </span><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">=&gt;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> 印表機設定</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">chronyd.service </span><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">=&gt;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> 時間校正 (<a href=\"http://technote.aven-network.com/821/using-chrony-adjust-clock\" target=\"_blank\">setup reference</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">daemons.service </span><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">=&gt;</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;系統服務(<a href=\"http://linux.vbird.org/linux_basic/0560daemons.php#daemon_type_init\" target=\"_blank\">鳥哥 - daemons系統服務</a> , <a href=\"http://www.osslab.tw/index.php?title=User:Alang/Linux_%26_UNIX_%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98/Linux_service_list_(%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8)/Linux_on_virtual_machine\" target=\"_blank\">OSSLap </a>)</span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/usr/lib/systemd/system/：每個服務最主要的啟動腳本設定，有點類似以前的 /etc/init.d 底下的檔案；</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/run/systemd/system/：系統執行過程中所產生的服務腳本，這些腳本的優先序要比 /usr/lib/systemd/system/ 高！</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/etc/systemd/system/：管理員依據主機系統的需求所建立的執行腳本，其實這個目錄有點像以前 /etc/rc.d/rc5.d/Sxx 之類的功能！執行優先序又比 /run/systemd/system/ 高喔！</span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>centOS 7 command</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">command (</span><a href=\"http://www.osslab.tw/index.php?title=User:Alang/Linux_%26_UNIX_%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98/Linux_service_list_(%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8)/Systemd_%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86(CentOS_7_%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">reference</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\">)</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>ssh 清除公鑰 （</strong>WARNING: REMOTE HOST IDENTIFICATION HAS CHANGED!&nbsp;<strong>）</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">清除方式（<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/zbrj12345/article/details/81942599\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a>）</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>version &amp; setup </strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">centOS 7 version content (<a href=\"http://blog.kevinlinul.idv.tw/?p=58\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">centOS 7 website (<a href=\"https://wiki.centos.org/zh-tw/Manuals/ReleaseNotes/CentOS7.1804?action=show&amp;redirect=zh-tw%2FManuals%2FReleaseNotes%2FCentOS7\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">centOS 7 install finish setup (<a href=\"http://blog.kevinlinul.idv.tw/?p=90\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>log service</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">vbird&#39;s linux - log (<a href=\"http://linux.vbird.org/linux_basic/0570syslog.php#analyze_vbird\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>system service (systemd service / systemctl command)</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">vbird&#39;s linux - sytemd command (<a href=\"http://linux.vbird.org/linux_basic/0560daemons.php\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">(( systemd path ))</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/usr/lib/systemd/system/ ： 每個服務最主要的啟動腳本設定，有點類似以前的 /etc/init.d 底下的檔案；</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/run/systemd/system/&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ：系統執行過程中所產生的服務腳本，這些腳本的優先序要比 /usr/lib/systemd/system/ 高！</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/etc/systemd/system/&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ：管理員依據主機系統的需求所建立的執行腳本，其實這個目錄有點像以前 /etc/rc.d/rc5.d/Sxx 之類的功能！執行優先序又比 /run/systemd/system/ 高喔！</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">(( vbird&#39;s limux import review ))</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">早期的服務管理使用 systemV 的機制，透過 /etc/init.d/*, service, chkconfig, setup 等指令來管理服務的啟動/關閉/預設啟動；</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">從 CentOS 7.x 開始，採用 systemd 的機制，此機制最大功能為平行處理，並採單一指令管理 (systemctl)，開機速度加快！</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">systemd 將各服務定義為 unit，而 unit 又分類為 service, socket, target, path, timer 等不同的類別，方便管理與維護</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">啟動/關閉/重新啟動的方式為： systemctl [start|stop|restart] unit.service</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">設定預設啟動/預設不啟動的方式為： systemctl [enable|disable] unit.service</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">查詢系統所有啟動的服務用 systemctl list-units --type=service 而查詢所有的服務 (含不啟動) 使用 systemctl list-unit-files --type=service</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">systemd 取消了以前的 runlevel 概念 (雖然還是有相容的 target)，轉而使用不同的 target 操作環境。常見操作環境為 multi-user.targer 與 graphical.target。 不重新開機而轉不同的操作環境使用 systemctl isolate unit.target，而設定預設環境則使用 systemctl set-default unit.target</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">systemctl 系統預設的設定檔主要放在 /usr/lib/systemd/system，管理員若要修改或自行設計時，則建議放在 /etc/systemd/system/ 目錄下。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">管理員應使用 man systemd.unit, man systemd.service, man systemd.timer 查詢 /etc/systemd/system/ 底下設定檔的語法， 並使用 systemctl daemon-reload 載入後，才能自行撰寫服務與管理服務喔！</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">除了 atd 與 crond 之外，可以 透過 systemd.timer 亦即 timers.target 的功能，來使用 systemd 的時間管理功能。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">一些不需要的服務可以關閉喔！</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><strong>20181019 (Linux , Software )</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>systemd 服務管理</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">OSSLab - systemd service manager (<a href=\"http://www.osslab.tw/index.php?title=User:Alang/Linux_%26_UNIX_%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98/Linux_service_list_(%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8)/Systemd_%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86(CentOS_7_%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4)\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">OSSLab - path /etc/systemd/system/</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>shell script</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">OSSLab - shell script demo (<a href=\"http://www.osslab.tw/index.php?title=User:Alang/Linux_%26_UNIX_%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98/Linux_SHELL\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>管理工具</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">OSSLab - 管理工具&nbsp;(<a href=\"http://www.osslab.tw/index.php?title=User:Alang/Linux_%26_UNIX_%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98/%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7//%E6%8B%BE%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%99%E6%85%A7\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>command - OSSLab (<a href=\"http://www.osslab.tw/index.php?title=User:Alang/Linux_%26_UNIX_%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98/CentOS_%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/Linux_%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E9%9B%86\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a>)</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">cd .. 回上一層</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">cd -&nbsp; 回上次的目錄</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">cd /&nbsp; 回根目錄</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">cd ~ 回自己帳號根目錄</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">modprobe 載入module , <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">會</span>處理載入的相依性問題 (<a href=\"https://blog.xuite.net/lidj37/twblog/179517568-modprobe+vs.+insmod+vs.+rmmod\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">insmod 載入module , <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">不會</span>處理載入的相依性問題 (<a href=\"https://blog.xuite.net/lidj37/twblog/179517568-modprobe+vs.+insmod+vs.+rmmod\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">rmmod 移除 module (<a href=\"https://blog.xuite.net/lidj37/twblog/179517568-modprobe+vs.+insmod+vs.+rmmod\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">lsmod , rmmod , modinfo check module information</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">modprobe</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">tar (<a href=\"http://note.drx.tw/2008/04/command.html\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">lspci find wireless wifi driver chipset (<a href=\"https://www.cyberciti.biz/faq/linux-find-wireless-driver-chipset/\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ll | wc -l <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> count all file amount</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">kill pid <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> del process&nbsp;</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">kill -p pid <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> force kill process</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">fdisk <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> 格式化 SD card (<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/Leezha/article/details/80083328\" target=\"_blank\">sd crad mmcblk0 : unknow partition table</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">fdisk hdd (<a href=\"https://blog.gtwang.org/linux/linux-add-format-mount-harddisk/\" target=\"_blank\">add new hdd</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">make , Makefile (<a href=\"https://dywang.csie.cyut.edu.tw/dywang/linuxProgram/node58.html\" target=\"_blank\">make command &amp; Makefile</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ubuntu <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> make kernel (<a href=\"https://www.ubuntu-tw.org/modules/newbb/viewtopic.php?post_id=350806\" target=\"_blank\">debian/ubuntu complier kerner</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ubuntu <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> apt / apt-get 差別 （<a href=\"https://www.sysgeek.cn/apt-vs-apt-get/\" target=\"_blank\">apt/apt-get 差別</a>）</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">vimdiff <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> vimdiff file1 file2 &nbsp;檔案比較</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">fldiff&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;&nbsp;</span>檔案比對 apt install fldiff - install</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">vim <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> replace 使用 (<a href=\"http://vim.wikia.com/wiki/Search_and_replace\" target=\"_blank\">replace 使用</a>）</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">swap 調整 (<a href=\"https://my.oschina.net/icebergxty/blog/1858336\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">grep 參數(<a href=\"http://huenlil.pixnet.net/blog/post/26326320-%5B%E8%BD%89%5Dgrep%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">nm , ar , objdump 編譯使用指令 (<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/princess9/article/details/6785108\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a>)</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">mkinitramfs <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;&nbsp;</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">unix2dos , dos2unix <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt; unix transfer dos format , dos transfer unix format</span></span></li>\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">硬體相關 (<a href=\"https://blog.longwin.com.tw/2014/02/linux-query-hardware-2014/\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a>&nbsp;, <a href=\"http://blog.51cto.com/feihan21/1174677\" target=\"_blank\">reference2</a>)</span></span></strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;記錄硬碟的部份, 有下述幾種指令可以使用:</span></p>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">sudo&nbsp;<strong>smartctl</strong>&nbsp;-i /dev/sda # 顯示硬碟型號及規格, apt-get install smartmontools</span>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Model Family:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Seagate Barracuda 7200.14 (AF)<br />\n	Device Model:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ST2000DM001-1CH164<br />\n	Serial Number:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Z1E3NQMJ<br />\n	LU WWN Device Id: 5 000c50 050533951<br />\n	Firmware Version: CC24<br />\n	User Capacity:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2,000,398,934,016 bytes [2.00 TB]<br />\n	Sector Sizes:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 512 bytes logical, 4096 bytes physical<br />\n	Rotation Rate:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 7200 rpm<br />\n	Device is:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; In smartctl database [for details use: -P show]<br />\n	ATA Version is:&nbsp;&nbsp; ATA8-ACS T13/1699-D revision 4<br />\n	SATA Version is:&nbsp; SATA 3.0, 6.0 Gb/s (current: 6.0 Gb/s)</span></p>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">sudo&nbsp;<strong>hdparm</strong>&nbsp;-i /dev/sda1 # apt-get install hdparm</span>\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/dev/sda1:</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Model=ST2000DM001-1CH164, FwRev=CC29, SerialNo=Z340PKFV<br />\n	Config={ HardSect NotMFM HdSw&gt;15uSec Fixed DTR&gt;10Mbs RotSpdTol&gt;.5% }<br />\n	RawCHS=16383/16/63, TrkSize=0, SectSize=0, ECCbytes=4<br />\n	BuffType=unknown, BuffSize=unknown, MaxMultSect=16, MultSect=16<br />\n	CurCHS=16383/16/63, CurSects=16514064, LBA=yes, LBAsects=3907029168<br />\n	IORDY=on/off, tPIO={min:120,w/IORDY:120}, tDMA={min:120,rec:120}<br />\n	PIO modes:&nbsp; pio0 pio1 pio2 pio3 pio4<br />\n	DMA modes:&nbsp; mdma0 mdma1 mdma2<br />\n	UDMA modes: udma0 udma1 udma2 udma3 udma4 udma5 *udma6<br />\n	AdvancedPM=yes: unknown setting WriteCache=enabled<br />\n	Drive conforms to: Reserved:&nbsp; ATA/ATAPI-4,5,6,7</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">* signifies the current active mode</span></p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">要看機器的其他硬體資訊, 有下述程式命令可以使用, 在此就不詳細介紹:</span></p>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">sudo&nbsp;<strong>dmidecode</strong>&nbsp;-t # 後面可以接下述的參數</span>\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">bios<br />\n	system<br />\n	baseboard<br />\n	chassis<br />\n	processor<br />\n	memory<br />\n	cache<br />\n	connector<br />\n	slot</span></p>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ex: sudo dmidecode -t memory # 列出 memory 詳細資訊</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">sudo dmidecode -t baseboard # 連主機板型號都會列出來</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">lshw</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">lspci # list all PCI devices</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">lspci -vv</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">lspci -nn</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">lsusb</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">dmesg # print or control the kernel ring buffer</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">lsusb # list USB devices</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/proc : process information pseudo-file system</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">tree -d /sys/devices</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">hostnamectl <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> display linux hostname detail content</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">cat /etc/os-release&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> display linux release info</span></li>\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">磁碟相關</span></span></strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">lsblk <span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> 列出所有磁碟明細</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">lscpu&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> 列出cpu明細</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">findmnt -t ext4&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> 列出mount device 明細 ex. -t ext4 只顯示format ext4&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">網路相關 centOS 7 新指令 - (<a href=\"http://linux.vbird.org/linux_server/0140networkcommand.php#ifconfig\" target=\"_blank\">鳥哥 ip command 說明</a>)</span></span></strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ip&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span> 替代 ifconfig 指令</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">效能相關&nbsp; (<a href=\"http://www.osslab.tw/index.php?title=User:Alang/Linux_%26_UNIX_%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98/Linux_%E6%95%88%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90-vmstat\" target=\"_blank\">OSSLap</a>)</span></span></strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">vmstat 2&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#FF0000\">=&gt;</span>&nbsp;每2秒顯示一次記憶體使用情況</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>remote desktop</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">ubuntu remote desktop (<a href=\"http://tomchun.tw/tomchun/2015/11/24/1-278/\" target=\"_blank\">references</a>)</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>minicom - terminal usb to rs232</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">minicom (<a href=\"http://yshsu168.blogspot.com/2007/10/linuxusbrs232.html\" target=\"_blank\">minicom 使用</a>)</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>mount</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">-su: /dev/sdc: Permission denied</span> (<a href=\"https://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=2250302\" target=\"_blank\">Error: &quot;dd: failed to open &#39;/dev/sdd&#39;: Permission denied&quot;</a>)</li>\n</ol>\n\n<ol>\n</ol>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong><span style=