"font-size:16px\">全部的modules</span>\n\n		<ul>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>Linux Driver - 目錄結構</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/proc</span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/devices</span>\n\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">裝置主編號:副編號</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/sys</span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/devices</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">裝置資訊</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/class</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">驅動資訊</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">/block</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">區塊裝置驅動資訊</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><strong>20190227</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>Linux Driver - 核心同步機制</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">中斷遮罩</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">不可分割操作</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">自旋鎖</span><span style=\"font-size:16px\">​​​​​​​​​​​​​​</span>​​​​​​​</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">旗號</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">BKL 大核心鎖</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><strong>20190226&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>Linux Driver</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/zhangjy6/p/5462644.html\" target=\"_blank\">reference</a>&nbsp;, </span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"http://rswiki.csie.org/dokuwiki/_media/courses:100_2:lab10_doc.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">demo driver paper reference</a></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"http://blog.logan.tw/2013/01/linux-driver.html\" target=\"_blank\">動手寫 linux Driver</a></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Makefile M要大寫， Makefile ，不能makefile&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">first install linux complier package</span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">install linux headers </span>\n\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">apt-get install linux-headers-$(uname -r)</span></span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">install linux kernel source</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">apt-get install linux-source</span></span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">linux kernel module complire step by step</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">need file <span style=\"color:#0000FF\">=&gt; test_module.c , Makefile&nbsp;</span></span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">test_module.c</span></span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">#include</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">#include</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">#include</span></li>\n				<li>&nbsp;</li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​static int test_module_init(void)</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">{</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;printk(KERN_ALERT &quot;test module init.&quot;);</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;return 0;</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">}</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">static void test_module_exit(exit)</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">{</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;printk(KERN_ALERT &quot;test module exit.&quot;);</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">}&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">module_init(test_module_init);</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">module_exit(test_module_exit);</span></li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Makefile</span></span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">obj-m := test_module.o</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">kernel_dir := /usr/src/linux-headers-$(shell uname -r)</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">all:</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;$(MAKE) -C $(kernel_dir)&nbsp;M=(shell pwd) modules</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">clean:</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;rm -rf *.o&nbsp;*.ko *.mod *.symvers *.order</span></li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">check module status</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">​​​​​​​​​​​​​​mount module&nbsp;</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">​​​​​​​insmos test_module.ko</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">unmount module</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">​​​​​​​rmmod test_module</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">check module&nbsp;</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">​​​​​​​dmesg <span style=\"color:#0000FF\">=&gt; show test_module mount and unmount status</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">lsmod | grep test_module <span style=\"color:#0000FF\">=&gt; show mdule from list</span></span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">建立裝置檔案</span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">​​​​​​​path <span style=\"color:#0000FF\">=&gt; mknod /dev/test_module c 60 0</span></span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">​​​​​​​​​​​​​​</span>test_module<span style=\"color:#0000FF\"> =&gt; 使用者自訂</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">c<span style=\"color:#0000FF\"> =&gt; char</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">60</span><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"> =&gt; 主要版本編號</span></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">0</span><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"> =&gt; 次要版本編號</span></span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">其中/dev/test_module 是裝置名稱，c 代表字元裝置，60 代表主要版本，0 代表次要版 本。當 driver 在向系統註冊的時候也必須用同樣的型態、名稱和主要版本註冊， 以免失敗。</span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">使用 driver</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">​​​​​​​​​​​​​​vim test.c</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">#include</span></li>\n		<li>&nbsp;</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">int main(void)</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">{</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;char buf[512];</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;FILE *fp = fopen(&quot;/dev/test_module&quot; , &quot;w+&quot;);</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;if(fp == NULL)</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;{</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; printf(&quot;can&#39;t open device. &quot;);</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; return 0;</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;else</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; {</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;printf(&quot;open device &quot;);</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;fread(buf , sizeof(buf) , 1 , fp);</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;fwrite(buf , sizeof(buf) , 1 , fp);</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;}</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">return 0;</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">}</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n','update','rl8002002','enable'),(54,'shelflife ','shelflife - 伺服器安裝的軟體','2019-03-19','<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\">20221102&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>CentOS 7</strong></span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Raid</strong></span>\n\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Raid 1 /boot 200MB</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Raid 1 SWAP 2GB</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Raid 10 4TB*4&nbsp;</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Raid&nbsp;10 4TB*2</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Samba</strong></span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">ver&nbsp;4.10.16</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<br />\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\">20190319&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><strong>Linux&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<ol style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>OS</strong></span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Ubuntu16.04</strong></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\