"https://software.intel.com/en-us/android/blogs/2013/12/06/building-ffmpeg-for-android-on-x86\" target=\"_blank\">intel porting android x86 - ffmpeg</a>&nbsp;</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://developer.android.com/ndk\" target=\"_blank\">NDK download</a></span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"http://www.ffmpeg.org/download.html\" target=\"_blank\">FFMPEG download</a></span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"http://www.itboth.com/d/RNruYv2myi6r/android-x86-ffmpeg\" target=\"_blank\">ffmpeg - android x86 編譯和優化</a></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"http://www.ihubin.com/blog/android-ffmpeg-demo-1/\" target=\"_blank\">ffmpeg - 編譯</a></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/fdad78aba1e7\" target=\"_blank\">ffmpeg - android x86 開發環境搭建</a></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/tanlon/archive/2012/04/26/2471550.html\" target=\"_blank\">ffmpeg - ubuntu10.04&nbsp;用 ndk6 編譯</a></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/c7bab9c020f0\" target=\"_blank\">ffmpeg - mac 編譯 ffmpeg for android x86 使用</a></span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://www.itread01.com/content/1548359645.html\" target=\"_blank\">Android 常用第三方庫</a></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">Linux 上</span></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">您需要為 readelf 安裝 binutils 程序包</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">ubuntu 18.04 apt install binutils&nbsp;</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">為 scanelf 安裝 pax-utils 程序包</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">ubuntu 18.04 apt install pax-utils</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-tw/tech/4o2e3g.html\" target=\"_blank\">Text Relocations reference 說明</a></span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"http://wiki.jikexueyuan.com/project/android-ndk-development-tutorial/android-mk-file.html\" target=\"_blank\">Android NDK 開發教程</a></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"http://david740204.pixnet.net/blog/post/447764498-ndk-build%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%83%E6%95%B8%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84\" target=\"_blank\">NDK 常用參數說明</a></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://codertw.com/android-%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC/27933/\" target=\"_blank\">android 動態載入so 檔要注意事項</a></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">android - 雙顯示</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"http://www.it610.com/article/4409534.htm\" target=\"_blank\">雙顯示</a></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"http://bluequiet.blogspot.com/2016/07/dual-screen-on-android-60.html\" target=\"_blank\">雙顯示 2</a></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://blog.stylingandroid.com/multiple-displays-part-2/\" target=\"_blank\">雙顯示 3</a>　</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/529755edc3c5\" target=\"_blank\">雙顯示 4 - android 6 以上要檢查SDK version</a>&nbsp;　</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/xiaoshubao/p/5630480.html\" target=\"_blank\">android - DisplayManager demo code&nbsp;</a></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/GooHong/article/details/8536102\" target=\"_blank\">android - Display Manager 服務解析</a></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">20190327</span></span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://medium.com/@xiuqige/%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BAlibxxx-so-text-relocations-exception-%E4%BB%A5zbar-libiconv%E7%82%BA%E4%BE%8B-89fe34415962\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">解決 text relocations 說明</span></a></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/bionic/+/master/android-changes-for-ndk-developers.md#text-relocations-enforced-for-api-level-23\" target=\"_blank\">詳細說明針對Android NDK修改</a></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/fd938a51b01f\" target=\"_blank\">dlopen 失敗 : 有文本定位</a></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/bionic/+/master/android-changes-for-ndk-developers.md#text-relocations-enforced-for-api-level-23\" target=\"_blank\">API &gt;= 23 時Android 處理狀況</a></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/bionic/+/master/android-changes-for-ndk-developers.md#text-relocations-enforced-for-api-level-23\" target=\"_blank\">test relocations&nbsp; 作用 ,&nbsp;代碼必須按原樣加載，不得修改。這種方法減少了加載時間並提高了安全性 , </a><em>潛在問題</em>：重定位強制執行代碼頁可寫，並浪費地增加內存中臟頁的數量。自Android K（API 19）以來，動態鏈接器已發出有關文本重定位的警告，但在API 23及更高版本上，它拒絕使用文本重定位加載代碼</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><em>解決方案</em>：將彙編程序重寫為獨立位置，以確保不需要進行文本重定位。</span></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">20190322</span></span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/technotes/guides/jni/spec/jniTOC.html\" target=\"_blank\">Oracle JNI 介紹</a></span></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">20190322</span></span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">Android .so readelf TEXT Relocations </span></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">&nbsp;20190321</span></span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/zhuyunier/article/details/78811948\" target=\"_blank\">.so readelf TEXT Relocations 說明定義</a></span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/shuaicike/article/details/78868772\" target=\"_blank\">NDK 重新編譯 .so 檔案</a>&nbsp;</span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#FF0000\">20190321</span></span>\n		<ol>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">Application.mk</span></span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">APP_ABI := x86</span></li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">Android.mk</span></span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">LOCAL_PATH := $(call my-dir)</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">include $(CLEAR_VARS)</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">LOCAL_MODULE&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;:= avcodec</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">LOCAL_SRC_FILES := libavcodec.so</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">LOCAL_LDFLAGS&nbsp; &nbsp; += -fPIC</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">include $(PREBUILT_SHARED_LIBRARY)</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">MESA_ENABLE_ASM := false</span></li>\n				<li>&nbsp;</li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">include $(CLEAR_VARS)</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">LOCAL_MODULE&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;:= avutil</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">LOCAL_SRC_FILES := libavutil.so</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">LOCAL_LDFLAGS&nbsp; &nbsp; += -fPIC</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">include $(PREBUILT_SHARED_LIBRARY)</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">MESA_ENABLE_ASM := false</span></li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">mkdir jni 目錄 , 把 Android.mk , Application.mk 放進去 , 執行 ndk-build</span></li>\n		</ol>\n		</li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">ffmpeg </span></span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">20190321</span></span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"https://ffmpeg.org/download.html#releases\" target=\"_blank\">ffmpeg 官網 download&nbsp;</a></span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">Android x86 </span></span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">20190321</span></span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><a href=\"http://clementyan.blogspot.com/2015/11/android-studio-import-so-file-so.html\" target=\"_blank\">Android studio import .so file 載入 so 檔案</a></span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">Android x86&nbsp;</span></span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">20190320</span></span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">libavcodec.so</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">libavutil.so</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">libswresample.so</span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">android-ndk-r15c , rebuild text relocations successful</span></li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">libglapi.so</span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">android-ndk-r15c , rebuild text reloacations boot fail</span></li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">solution&nbsp;</span></span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">reference</span></span>\n				<ul>\n					<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/28357706/android-ndk-linking-x86-shared-library\" target=\"_blank\">Android ndk - 連接x86庫共享</a></span></span></li>\n					<li><span style=\"font