de</span></p>\n\n				<ul>\n					<li>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">File 1 main page</span></p>\n\n					<ul>\n						<li>\n						<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">FragmentManager fm = getSupportFragmentManager();</span></p>\n						</li>\n						<li>\n						<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">FragmentTransaction fragmentTransaction = fm.beginTransaction();</span></p>\n						</li>\n						<li>\n						<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Fragment btn8_add_stock_record = new btn8_add_stock_record();<br />\n						fragmentTransaction.replace(R.id.layout_list , btn8_add_stock_record);<br />\n						fragmentTransaction.commit();</span></div>\n						</li>\n					</ul>\n					</li>\n					<li>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">File 2 second page</span></p>\n\n					<ul>\n						<li>\n						<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\">@Override public View onCreateView(LayoutInflater inflater , ViewGroup container , Bundle SavedInstanceState){ Log.d(TAG, &quot;onCreateView.&quot;); return inflater.inflate(R.layout.activity_btn8_add_stock_record , container , false); }</span></p>\n						</li>\n					</ul>\n					</li>\n				</ul>\n				</li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">JNI , NDK&nbsp;</span></span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">20200305</span></span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><a href=\"https://wiki.jikexueyuan.com/project/jni-ndk-developer-guide/function.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">JNI 開發指南&nbsp;</span></a></li>\n			<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/anhenzhufeng/article/details/78913341\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">android studio loading *.jar / *. so 檔案</span></a></li>\n			<li><a href=\"https://codertw.com/%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F%E8%AA%9E%E8%A8%80/655777/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Android進階3：Android的NDK開發JNI基礎</span></a></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">20200303&nbsp;</span></span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><a href=\"https://8085studio.wordpress.com/2015/04/25/android-studio-ndk-jni/#method_1\" target=\"_blank\">android studio JNI ndk build</a>&nbsp;</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">&nbsp;開新 APK 增加 ndk module 路徑</span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">build.gradle</span>\n				<ul>\n					<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">defaultconfig</span>\n					<ul>\n						<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\">ndk{ moduleName &quot;jni_test&quot; }</span></li>\n						<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\">sourceSets.main.jni.srcDirs = [ ]</span></li>\n					</ul>\n					</li>\n				</ul>\n				</li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">local.properties</span>\n				<ul>\n					<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">ndk.dir=/root/Android/ndk/android-ndk-r20</span></li>\n				</ul>\n				</li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">選Project 顯示模式 , 在app / src / main /&nbsp;java &gt; 新增資料夾 jni &gt; 新增 Android.mk / Application.mk / jni_test.c</span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Android.mk</span>\n				<ul>\n					<li>\n					<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:12px\">LOCAL_PATH := $(call my-dir)\n\ninclude $(CLEAR_VARS)\n\nLOCAL_MODULE := jni_test\nLOCAL_SRC_FILES := jni_test.c io.c\n\nLOCAL_LDLIBS := -llog -landroid -lEGL -lGLESv1_CM\n\ninclude $(BUILD_SHARED_LIBRARY)</span></pre>\n					</li>\n				</ul>\n				</li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Application.mk</span>\n				<ul>\n					<li><span style=\"font-size:12px\">APP_ABI := all</span></li>\n				</ul>\n				</li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">jni_test.c</span></li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\">在app / src / main /&nbsp;java &nbsp;新增 jni_java.java&nbsp;</span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:14px\">static {</span>\n				<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:14px\">    </span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">try{\n        System.loadLibrary(&quot;j