"color:#0000FF\">股票用語</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">資本公債</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<h1><a href=\"https://rich01.com/what-is-additional-paid-in-capital/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">股票財報》什麼是資本公積(Additional Paid In Capital)？如何查詢？對配息有什麼影響？</span></a></h1>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">保留盈餘</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<h1><a href=\"https://rich01.com/what-is-retained-earnings/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">股票財報》什麼是保留盈餘(Retained Earnings)？與股利有什麼關係？盈餘負數或增加代表什麼？</span></a></h1>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">損益表</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<h1><a href=\"https://rich01.com/what-is-income-statement/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1分鐘看懂財務報表》損益表(Income Statement)怎麼看？營收、費用、淨利介紹</span></a></h1>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">營業現金流</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<h1><a href=\"https://rich01.com/what-operating-cash-flow/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">營業現金流量是什麼、如何計算？如何用它來分析公司營運</span></a></h1>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">現金流量表</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<h1><a href=\"https://rich01.com/what-cash-flow-statement/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1分鐘看懂財務報表》現金流量表(Cash Flow Statement)怎麼看？營業、投資、融資現金流解析</span></a></h1>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">資產報酬率</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<h1><a href=\"https://rich01.com/what-is-roa/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">資產報酬率ROA是什麼？公式如何計算？ROA與ROE有什麼差異？</span></a></h1>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">負債權益比</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<h1><a href=\"https://rich01.com/what-is-debt-to-equity-ratio/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">負債權益比(Debt-To-Equity Ratio)是什麼？負債越低真的越好嗎？如何查詢？</span></a></h1>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">本益比成長</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><a href=\"https://rich01.com/ratio-peg/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">一分鐘看懂本益成長比(PEG)：本益成長比查詢與公式？本益成長比選股要注意什麼？</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">淨利</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">營利利益是公司營運本業所賺的錢</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">淨利是營業利益加上業外損益(可能是虧損或賺錢)的總和</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">業外損益</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">收益</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">利息</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">股利</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">處分資產收益</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">投資收益</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">利率補貼</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">租金</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">損失</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">借貸利息</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">投資損失</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">處分資產損失</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">又分稅前淨利(稅前純益)，稅後淨利(稅後純益)</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">營業利益</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">等於營業收入 - 營業成本，再加上營業費用後的利潤。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">營業費用就是產品銷售的間接成本</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">包含管理費用</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">員工薪資</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">各項租金</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">折舊費</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">推銷費用</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">廣告費</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">業務獎金</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">型錄DM費用</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">研發費用</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">新產品</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">設備開發</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">研發人員獎金</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">毛利</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">等於營業收入 - 營業成本後的利潤。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">營業(直接)成本包含與產品直接相關的物料進貨費用，製造費用，營業成本的分類依產業業別爾有所差異。</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">股東權益報酬率 ROE</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">又叫淨值報酬率 ROE ，Return On Equity ，股本報酬率，股權收益率，股本收益率等。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">ROE是用來衡量股東投資報酬率，反映公司利用資產淨值產生淨利(純益)的能力。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">ROE越高，表示公司獲利能力越強。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">如果總資產不變，總負債增加，股東權益就會減少，而帶動ROE上升。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">ROE另一參考指標，</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>ROA 資產報酬率 Return On Assets</strong></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">當ROA(%)，大於債務的利率(%)時，ROA = 稅後淨利 / 總資產 ， 債務增加才能使ROE有正面效益。</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">股東權益</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">又叫淨值或股東權益總額。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">等於 總資產 - 總負債 後所剩餘的金額，也是公司的自有資本，或是股東投資公司的錢。</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">總負債</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">又叫負債總額</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">包含一年內短期借款，應付帳款，應付票據，預收款項等流動負債。</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">以及長期借款，遞延所得等非流動性資產。</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">總資產</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">又叫資產總計或資產總額</span>，<span style=\"font-size:18px\">等於權益總額 + 負債總額，也等於流動資產+非流動資產。</span></li>\n	<li><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\">總資產 = 權益總額 + 負債總額&nbsp;</span></strong>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">(股東)權益總額</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">股本</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">保留盈餘</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">資本公債</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">庫藏股票</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">負債總額</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">​​​​​​​​​​​​​​流動負債</span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">​​​​​​​短期借款</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">應付票據</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">應付帳款</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">其他</span></li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">非流動負債</span>\n			<ul>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">​​​​​​​長期借款</span></li>\n				<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">遞延所得稅負債及其他</span></li>\n			</ul>\n			</li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n	<li><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\">總資產 = 流動資產 + 非流動資產</span></strong></li>\n	<li>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">流動資產</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">​​​​​​​​​​​​​​現金</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">存貨</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">預付款</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">應收票據</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">應收帳款</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">其他</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">非流動資產</span>\n		<ol>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">​​​​​​​不動產</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">廠房</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">設備</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">投資性資產</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">無形資產</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">遞延所得稅資產</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">其他</span></li>\n		</ol>\n		</li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n','update','rl8002002','enable'),(143,'唸書 ','唸書 - 閱讀書單','2021-03-05','<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">知識 - 閱讀書單</span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">創業</span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">202011</span>\n\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">富爸爸窮爸爸</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">富爸爸窮爸爸2</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">金融保險</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">202101</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">投資型保險商品題庫</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">股票</span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">202101</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">股票收租法我4年鑽100%</span></li>\n			<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">不看盤投資術</span></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n','server','rl8002002','enable'),(144,'投資 ','投資 - 股票 8 - 持股分析','2021-03-09','<p><span style=\"font-size:22px\">投資 - 股票 8 - 持股分析</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:22px\">20210721</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">買進後用六指標定期檢視</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">財務品質</span></span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">ROE&gt;10％ or 12%</span></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">營業利益率&gt;0%</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">營業活動現金流量&gt;0</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">市場面</span></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">估價沒有超漲</span></span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"color: