um 安裝</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">20210911</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">在VM中非預期的情況中增減網卡時會出現網路服務異常須進行以下步驟,來重新設定網路環境</span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">刪除網路MAC設定</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">rm -rf /etc/udev/rules.d/70-persistent-net.rules</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">清除ifcfg中的MAC及UUID設定值</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">重開機</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Cat /etc/udev/rules.d/70-persistent-net.rules</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:27pt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">確認HWADDR&nbsp;,&nbsp;並加回ifcfg-ethx中</span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">uuidgen eth0 ,並將該數值加回ifcfg-ethx中</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">在來restart network service即可</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">不過Linux預設會有兩種網路管理程式,若沒設定好重起網路服務會出現&quot; RTNETLINK answers: File exists&quot;&nbsp;訊息。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">請先將服務停止</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">/sbin/service NetworkManager stop</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">/sbin/service network stop</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">在選擇一個啟動就好</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">/sbin/service network start</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">調整開機順序避免問題再次發生</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">chkconfig --level 35 network on</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">chkconfig --level 0123456 NetworkManager off</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">如果之後啟動後網路可連線，但出現</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">bring up interface&nbsp; ip address is already in use for device eth0&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">這時在網卡設定檔中加上不檢查&nbsp;ARP</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">vi /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth0</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">ARPCHECK=no</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">reference</span></span></p>\n\n<h2><a href=\"https://my.esecuredata.com/index.php?/knowledgebase/article/4/add-or-replace-a-network-adapter-nic-on-centos-6\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\">Add or Replace a Network Adapter (NIC) on CentOS 6</span></a></h2>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">更改NIC方式</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">GUI</span></span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">system-config-network</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">command</span></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">vim /etc/systemconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth*&nbsp; ，換掉 MAC 及 UUID , 改完重啟設定</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">service network restart or /etc/init.d/network restart</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.cxyzjd.com/article/qq_42183962/110954347\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">CentOS6安装rpm时报错&ldquo;Cannot find a valid baseurl for repo: centos-sclo-rh&ldquo;的解决办法_梦马韶华-程序员宅基地</span></a></p>\n','update','rl8002002','enable'),(152,'網頁框架 ','網頁框架 - php Laravel','2021-06-26','<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">網頁框架 - php Laravel 8.0 版本以上</span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">外部ip連進laravel 網站</span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">php artisan serv --Host 192.168.50.199 --port 8000</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">php artisan serv --Host 0.0.0.0</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n','server','rl8002002','enable'),(153,'唸書 ','唸書 - 金融系列','2021-07-07','<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">股魚最強存股秘技</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">2021