_RTS</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td>\n				<pre>\n<span style=\"font-size:18px\">go config data_collect -rt_conv_bucket enable\n</span></pre>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			<tr>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">CONV_RTU CONV_RTS</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"3\">\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">NX: Network -&gt; Configuration</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">&ldquo;Servers&rdquo; tab: Add the BI IPs to the &ldquo;Allowed Hosts&rdquo; list</span></p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			<tr>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">SDR, UDR</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">&ldquo;SMP&rdquo; tab -&gt; &ldquo;Policy and Charging&rdquo;: SDR Collection Status=On</span></p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			<tr>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">HTTP</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">&ldquo;Integrated Service&rdquo; tab: HTTP Monitoring=Always Enabled</span></p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			<tr>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">HDR</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"3\">\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">NX: SG -&gt; Configuration -&gt; &ldquo;Service Activation&rdquo; tab</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">HDR Generation Enablement=Enabled</span></p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			<tr>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">VDR</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">VDR Generation Enablement=Enabled</span></p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			<tr>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">MOU</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">VoIP Data Collection=Enabled</span></p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			<tr>\n				<td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\">\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">NS...</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">NetworkSecure Central Manager</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Enabled upon installation: Central Reporter (CRM), Local Reporter (LRM)</span></p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			<tr>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">NetworkSecure Filter</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Enabled upon installation: Local Reporter (LRM)</span></p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n			<tr>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">CMDR</span></p>\n				</td>\n				<td>&nbsp;</td>\n				<td>\n				<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Enabled upon CMTS Awareness configuration</span></p>\n				</td>\n			</tr>\n		</tbody>\n	</table>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"font-size:22px\"><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">Configure DM network Parameters</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Network parameters configuration netmenu.sh</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">2. Setup Data Mediator parameters dev_setup.sh &ndash;m datamediation</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">3. Reboot<br />\n	go config reboot</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">4. Set up High Availability (if relevant)</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">&ldquo;netmenu.sh&rdquo; will configure the following parameters</span></p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">running the netmenu.sh script:</span></span></p>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Data Mediator IP and mask</span></p>\n		</li>\n		<li>\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Data Mediator Gateway IP for network access</span></p>\n		</li>\n		<li>\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">DNS Server IP</span></p>\n		</li>\n		<li>\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Host name</span></p>\n		</li>\n		<li>\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">NTP Time Server IP</span></p>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">Bucket Data Types</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">CONV &ndash; Conversation. Include bandwidth per connection.<br />\n	CONV_RTU - Real Time Unsolicited. RT information per policy with drill down to applications.</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">CONV_RTS - Real Time Solicited. RT information of specific conversation/application for specific user/IP.<br />\n	SDR - Session Detail Record. Information extracted from the RADIUS message.<br />\n	UDR - Usage Detail Record. Volume per subscriber and per application within a session (YouTube, skype, FTP, P2P...).</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">HTTP - HTTP Domain. Web traffic information (number of connections/subscribers/BW) per HTTP Domain.<br />\n	HDR - HTTP Detail Records. They include web activity usage per subscriber.<br />\n	VDR - Video Data Records. Video session (response time, hourly volume, resolution). VC - Virtual Channel. Include bandwidth per policy element: LineID/PipeID/VCID. MOU - Minutes of Use. VOIP usage information (session duration, start and end times).<br />\n	CMDR - Cable Modem Data Record.<br />\n	NS... - Group of buckets generated by users/subscriber activity in NetworkSecure.</span></p>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">Snapshot file</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Creating Snapshot File</span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Service Gateway</span></span></p>\n\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">&bull; SG Snapshot command : snapshot</span>&nbsp;</p>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">snapshot SG Snapshot location :&nbsp;&nbsp;/opt/allot/snapshots/ snapshot.system.date_time.tgz</span></p>\n\n		<p><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">NetXplorer</span></span></p>\n\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">&bull; NX Snapshot command :&nbsp;create_snapshot_logs.sh</span></p>\n\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">&bull; NX Snapshot location: /opt/allot/tmp/snapshot_.tar.gz</span></p>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">Allot verify License Key</span></span>​​​​​</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">verify SG License key</span></span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">go config view key</span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">verify NX License key</span></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">open NetXplorer&nbsp;</span>\n		<ul>\n			<li>\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Tools &rarr; NetXplorer Application&nbsp;&rarr;&nbsp;Server Registration</span></p>\n			</li>\n			<li>\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Check Activation Key</span></p>\n			</li>\n			<li>\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Check Expiration Date</span></p>\n			</li>\n			<li>\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Validate Enabled Features</span></p>\n			</li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">Allot blade command</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">The acstat CLI command gives you a quick view of the connection status</span>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">acstat</span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\">acstat -ix</span></li>\n		<li>\n		<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\">\n			<caption>\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Allot SG blade command</span></span></p>\n			</caption>\n			<tbody>\n				<tr>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">acstat -l line</span></p>\n					</td>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">View number of open connections on each Line</span></p>\n					</td>\n				</tr>\n				<tr>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">acstat -l pipe</span></p>\n					</td>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">View number of open connections on each Pipe</span></p>\n					</td>\n				</tr>\n				<tr>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">acstat -l vc</span></p>\n					</td>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">View number of open connections on each Virtual Channel</span></p>\n					</td>\n				</tr>\n				<tr>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">acstat -l server</span></p>\n					</td>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">View servers currently being used for steering</span></p>\n					</td>\n				</tr>\n			</tbody>\n		</table>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Is Bandwidth Allocated Correctly?</span></p>\n\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">To show the bandwidth on each link command : acmon</span></p>\n		</li>\n		<li>\n		<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\">\n			<caption><span style=\"color:#0000FF\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Allot SG blade bandwidth command </span></span></caption>\n			<tbody>\n				<tr>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">acmon -l </span></p>\n					</td>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Monitor throughput of a specific line</span></p>\n					</td>\n				</tr>\n				<tr>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">acmon -p </span></p>\n					</td>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Monitor throughput of a specific pipe</span></p>\n					</td>\n				</tr>\n				<tr>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">acmon -v </span></p>\n					</td>\n					<td>\n					<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Monitor throughput of a specific VC</span></p>\n					</td>\n				</tr>\n			</tbody>\n		</table>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\">Allot the elements synchronized for NTP Ser